@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ybswem(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.cos(((v0 + 0.30 / tmp + 0.91) - wp.sin(v0 + 0.31)))
    tmp = (v0 * (0.52 / wp.exp(tmp + 0.56)))
    tmp = (wp.exp((v0 + 0.47 - v2 + 0.88)) * 0.59)
    v1 = wp.cos(0.62)
    v2 = (wp.sin(v0) / v1)
    v0 = wp.exp(tmp)
    data[tid] = v0
